---
import MarketingLayout from '../components/layout/MarketingLayout.astro'
---

<MarketingLayout title="FAQ">
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
          FAQ
        </span>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-900">
          Pertanyaan Umum
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-neutral-500 text-lg">
          Jawaban untuk pertanyaan yang sering ditanyakan
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-3">
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-neutral-100 overflow-hidden">
          <summary class="p-6 cursor-pointer font-semibold text-neutral-900 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-inset rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-between">
            <span>Bagaimana cara membeli mangga?</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-neutral-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-sm text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            Buat akun sebagai Konsumen, lalu browse marketplace untuk memilih produk yang diinginkan.
            Tambahkan ke keranjang, pilih alamat pengiriman, dan lakukan pembayaran.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-neutral-100 overflow-hidden">
          <summary class="p-6 cursor-pointer font-semibold text-neutral-900 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-inset rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-between">
            <span>Apakah mangga dijamin segar?</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-neutral-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-sm text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            Ya! Semua mangga dikirim langsung dari kebun petani saat masih segar. Kami menggunakan
            packing khusus untuk menjaga kesegaran selama pengiriman.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-neutral-100 overflow-hidden">
          <summary class="p-6 cursor-pointer font-semibold text-neutral-900 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-inset rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-between">
            <span>Bagaimana cara menjadi petani di ManggaKu?</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-neutral-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-sm text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            Daftar sebagai Petani, lengkapi data diri, unggah dokumen verifikasi (KTP dan foto lahan),
            dan tunggu persetujuan admin. Setelah diverifikasi, kamu bisa mulai menjual produk.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-neutral-100 overflow-hidden">
          <summary class="p-6 cursor-pointer font-semibold text-neutral-900 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-inset rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-between">
            <span>Metode pembayaran apa saja yang diterima?</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-neutral-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-sm text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            Kami menerima GoPay, OVO, QRIS, Transfer Bank, dan COD (Bayar di Tempat).
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-neutral-100 overflow-hidden">
          <summary class="p-6 cursor-pointer font-semibold text-neutral-900 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-inset rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-between">
            <span>Bagaimana jika produk yang diterima tidak sesuai?</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-neutral-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-sm text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            Kamu bisa mengajukan komplain melalui halaman pesanan. Tim kami akan membantu
            mediasi antara pembeli dan penjual untuk menyelesaikan masalah.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-neutral-100 overflow-hidden">
          <summary class="p-6 cursor-pointer font-semibold text-neutral-900 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-inset rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-between">
            <span>Berapa biaya pengiriman?</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-neutral-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-sm text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            Biaya pengiriman dihitung berdasarkan jarak dan berat paket. Detail biaya akan ditampilkan
            saat proses checkout sebelum kamu melakukan pembayaran.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex flex-col items-center gap-4 p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white rounded-3xl border border-primary-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Pertanyaan lainnya?</p>
          <a
            href="/kontak"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 rounded-xl hover:from-primary-700 hover:to-primary-800 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-primary-500/25 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-offset-2 min-h-[44px]"
          >
            Hubungi Kami
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MarketingLayout>
